In a disturbing incident that took place in the sacred hills of Uttarakhand, two individuals responsible for operating horses were caught on camera coercing an animal to smoke a substance. This cruel act towards the horse has garnered attention from animal lovers and netizens, who shared the video online and brought it to the notice of the police authorities.

The video is both distressing and alarming, as it raises concerns regarding the safety of tourists and pilgrims who rely on these horses for transportation. Furthermore, the inhumane behavior exhibited by the horse operators undoubtedly poses health risks for the animals involved.

Despite the horse's attempts to avoid the rolled weed, the perpetrators forcefully expose it to the substance by inserting it close to the horse's nostrils. The duo can be observed tightly holding and closing the horse's mouth, ensuring that it ingests the intoxicant.

In response to the viral video, the Uttarakhand Police acknowledged the incident through a tweet, stating that they are actively investigating the matter. "We have taken note of the viral video depicting the forceful administration of smoke to a horse. We are currently working to identify the individuals seen in the video," the police department conveyed.

SERANG – Dinas Ketahanan Pangan dan Pertanian (DKPP) Kabupaten Serang memastikan hewan qurban seperti kambing, domba, sapi dan kerbau yang tersebar di 29 kecamatan dalam keadaan sehat.

Hal itu dilakukan Pemantauan dan pendataan terkait kondisi hewan tersebut dilakukan sejak hewan kurban didatangkan ke Kabupaten Serang.

Kepala DKPP Kabupaten Serang Suhardjo mengatakan untuk memastikan keberadaan hewan kurban dalam kondisi sehat, pihaknya teliti dalam melakukan pemantauan.

Pemantauan tak hanya dilakukan sejak didatangkan dari luar daerah, hingga hewan qurban sampai di tangan pelanggan.

⚠️ Groundbreaking report #Trashion reveals the devastating impact of exporting waste plastic clothes to the Global South.

🇰🇪 Up to 300 million items of synthetic clothing are dumped in Kenya each year, fueling the plastic pollution crisis. This is the result of the growing production of cheap, synthetic clothing made by brands in the Global North.

👚Over 1 in 3 pieces of used clothing shipped to Kenya contain plastic and immediately become waste. This is despite restrictions on plastic waste export around the world.

🇰🇪 The system of used-clothing trade is burdening communities and the environment in the receiving countries. It’s time for brands to take action and end the cycle of fast fashion and waste.

🚢 The export of used clothing has become the export of plastic waste. Layers of clothing and other waste can be seen at Dandora dumpsite in Kenya, a testament to the damage caused by fast fashion.

🚨 Sorting at the source is failing, and many recycling companies are involved in the used-clothing trade. It’s time for these companies to live up to their sustainability claims and drive greater circularity.

🧵 The impacts of microplastic leaching and environmental contamination are likely to be significant, as a large proportion of used clothing ends up dumped on landfills and pollutes the Nairobi River. We must act now to prevent further damage.

It’s time to end #fossilfashion 👗

Zambia has reached a historic deal to restructure its $6.3 billion debt with official creditors, including China. This is a major step toward economic recovery and growth for the country. Here are three takeaways from this landmark agreement:
- Zambia is the first African nation to default on its sovereign debt during the COVID-19 pandemic and the first to successfully negotiate debt relief under the G20 framework.

- China, as the largest official creditor to Zambia, played a crucial role in the deal, showing its willingness to cooperate with other lenders and support debt sustainability in Africa.
- The deal paves the way for private sector creditors to follow suit and restructure the $6.8 billion owed to them by Zambia, easing the burden on the country's finances.

आदिपुरुष को लेकर विवाद बढ़ते ही जा रहे हैं। रामानंद सागर की ‘रामायण’ में काम करने वाले सभी कलाकारों ने फिल्म ‘आदिपुरुष’ के डायलॉग्स और कहानी को लेकर अपनी निराशा व्यक्त की। इसके अलावा सिने वर्क एसोसिएशन से जुड़े लोगों ने फिल्म की पीएम मोदी से ये गुजारिश की थी कि फिल्म की स्क्रीनिंग को तुरंत रोका जाए, यहां तक कि फ्यूचर में भी फिल्म को रिलीज न किया जाए।
हालांकि, फिल्म के विवादों का असर इंडिया में साफ तौर पर देखने को मिला, लेकिन वर्ल्डवाइड अब भी ओम राउत के निर्देशन में बनी ये फिल्म अपनी सफलता का परचम लहरा रही है। छह दिनों में ही ‘आदिपुरुष’ ने दुनियाभर में काफी अच्छी कमाई कर ली है।
आदिपुरुष के खिलाफ बढ़ते हुए विवाद को देखकर मेकर्स ने फिल्म में हनुमान जी के डायलॉग्स में बदलाव किये हैं, लेकिन इसके बाद भी कई चीजें हैं, जिसे लेकर लोग आपत्ति जता रहे हैं। घरेलू बॉक्स ऑफिस पर तो फिल्म की कमाई में वर्किंग डेज पर गिरावट देखने को मिली, लेकिन दुनियाभर में फिल्म को काफी पसंद किया जा रहा है।
लगभग 500 करोड़ के बजट में बनी ‘आदिपुरुष‘ ने दुनियाभर में 400 करोड़ का आंकड़ा पार कर गुरुवार यानी कि छठे दिन तक 410 करोड़ की कमाई कर ली है। ग्लोबल स्तर पर ये फिल्म जिस तरह से कमाई कर रही है, उसे देखते हुए ये कहना गलत नहीं होगा कि फिल्म जल्द ही अपना बजट निकाल सकती है।

आदिपुरुष इंडिया के अलावा न्यूजीलैंड-ऑस्ट्रेलिया, यूएस सहित कई अलग-अलग देशों में मेकर्स ने रिलीज की। एडवांस बुकिंग में ही फिल्म ने कन्नड़ के रॉकिंग स्टार यश का रिकॉर्ड की केजीएफ का रिकॉर्ड ब्रेक कर दिया था। इस फिल्म ने दुनियाभर में पहले ही दिन 140 करोड़ की टोटल कमाई की थी।
 
दूसरे दिन ओवरसीज ओम राउत की फिल्म ने 240 करोड़, तीसरे दिन 340 करोड़, चौथे दिन 375 करोड़ और पांचवें दिन 395 करोड़ का वर्ल्डवाइड बिजनेस किया। इसके बाद फिल्म छठे दिन भी दुनियाभर में अपनी सफलता का डंका बजाने में सफल रही। आदिपुरुष के पास अब भी ये वीकेंड कमाई के लिए बाकी है, देखना है कि रविवार तक फिल्म दुनियाभर में अपना मैजिक चलाने में सफल होती है या नहीं।

मणिपुर में हिंसा की घटना थमने का नाम नहीं ले रही है। राज्य से प्रत्येक दिन हिंसा की खबरें सामने आ रही है। इसी बीच भारतीय सेना के स्पीयर कोर ने बताया कि हिंसा की घटनाओं में दो सैनिक घायल हो गए हैं। इंफाल पश्चिम जिले के एन बोलजांग में बदमाशों ने गोलीबारी की। इस गोलीबारी में दो सैनिकों को मामूली चोटें आईं। उन्होंने कहा कि दोनों सैनिकों की हालत स्थिर है। सुरक्षा बल द्वारा तलाशी के दौरान एक इंसास लाइट मशीन गन बरामद की गई।
मणिपुर में हिंसा थम नहीं रही है, जिसे देखते हुए सरकार अलर्ट है। केंद्रीय गृह मंत्री अमित शाह ने मणिपुर की स्थिति को लेकर 24 जून को सर्वदलीय बैठक बुलाई है। उन्होंने मणिपुर के हालात पर चर्चा के लिए राष्ट्रीय राजधानी नई दिल्ली में शनिवार को तीन बजे बैठक बुलाई है।
इधर, मणिपुर में हिंसा को देखते हुए इंटरनेट पर 25 जून तक के लिए प्रतिबंध बढ़ा दिया गया है। हिंसा की गतिविधि को रोकने के लिए इंटरनेट सेवाओं पर प्रतिबंध लगाया गया है। 
मणिपुर में मैतेई और कुकी समुदायों के बीच एक महीने पहले हिंसा भड़क गई। इस हिंसा में 100 से अधिक लोगों की मौत हो चुकी है।

Suzuki India is set to expand its product portfolio soon with the V-Strom 800DE. Two test mules of this upcoming ADV were spotted testing in Gurgaon and these spy shots have revealed plenty of details. 

The Suzuki V-Strom 800DE will be the successor to the 650cc model currently on sale. It’ll feature a vertically stacked LED headlight topped by a transparent visor, a beak below it, a wide handlebar with a guard, and a single-piece seat.

The list of features on the Suzuki V-Strom 800DE will comprise LED illumination, a five-inch TFT, traction control, ride-by-wire, low RPM assist, a bi-directional quickshifter, ABS, ride modes, and more. 

We expect Suzuki India to debut the bike close to the end of this year with an asking price of around Rs. 12 lakh (ex-showroom). Once launched, it’ll have the Triumph Tiger 900 and the BMW F850 GS as its rivals.

Despite Hajj being mandatory to only physically and financially capable Muslims, a Pakistani pilgrim has overcome physical challenges and is ready to perform Hajj, the pilgrimage to Mecca.

Mohammed Shafiq, 43, travelled all the way from Pakistan to fulfill his dream of completing the fifth pillar of Islam despite having one leg amputated.

Shafiq’s leg was amputated 30 years ago when he was run over by a bus. However, his spirits remained unshaken as he held on to the dream of making the sacred pilgrimage to Mecca. After years of saving money, Shafiq’s dream finally came true this year.

Speaking to Arabic media, Shafiq shared how losing his leg fuelled an undying enthusiasm and optimism within him to undertake this obligatory duty. He expressed immense joy and pleasure at having made it to the holy city and mentioned that he is eagerly counting minutes and hours in anticipation of the Day of Arafat.

“I will throw pebbles myself during the days of Tashreeq, leaning on my crutch. My feeling is indescribable, and I see the Kaaba, the focal point of Muslims, in front of my eyes. The dream I have been waiting for all my life is coming true,” Shafiq said with emotions running high.

हरियाणा के रोहतक जिले के सांपला में चौधरी छोटूराम स्मारक स्थल पर गुरुवार को एक किसान महापंचायत हुई। इस महापंचायत में पूर्व राज्यपाल सत्यपाल मलिक भी पहुंचे। इस दौरान उन्होंने कहा कि जब-जब विपक्ष एकजुट हुआ है बीजेपी को हार का सामना करना पड़ा है। उन्होंने कहा कि इस बार बीजेपी के सामने विपक्ष का एक ही उम्मीदवार रहने वाला है। इसके लिए योजना बना ली गई है। मलिक ने कहा कि विपक्ष के पास इस समय 10 उम्मीदवार सीएम बनने के लायक हैं।
पूर्व राज्यपाल सत्यपाल मलिक से जब मीडिया ने चुनाव लड़ने के लिए पूछा तो उन्होंने कहा कि वो ना ही किसी पार्टी में जाएंगे और ना ही चुनाव लड़ेगें, लेकिन बीजेपी को जो भी हराएगा वो उसकी मदद करेंगे। वहीं पीएम चेहरे को लेकर मलिक से पूछा गया कि पीएम के तौर पर कौन सबसे अच्छा चेहरा हो सकता है। इसपर मलिक ने कहा कि सबसे बढ़िया चेहरा तो प्रधानमंत्री के लिए मैं हूं।

पहलवानों के मुद्दे  पर पूर्व राज्यपाल मलिक ने बीजेपी सरकार को घेरते हुए कहा कि बीजेपी को सिर्फ सत्ता से मतलब है बाकि किसी की कोई परवाह नहीं है। वहीं मलिक पुलवामा मामले की जांच को लेकर भी सवाल उठाया उन्होंने कहा कि सरकार ने अभी तक पुलवामा मामले की जांच क्यों नहीं करवाई है। 
पूर्व राज्यपाल सत्यपाल मलिक जिस किसान महापंचायत में शामिल होने के लिए सांपला में चौधरी छोटूराम स्मारक स्थल पहुंचे थे वहां पिछले एक साल से अग्निवीर योजना, एमएसपी की गारंटी, महिलाओं को न्याय दिलाने के लिए धरना चल रहा है।

In a tragic fire mishap that took place on April 29 in Balapur, a newly set up wholesale grocery shop was burnt to ashes due to an alleged short circuit.

Mohd Abul Hasan who is the owner of Harmain Traders, lost everything he owned as he invested nearly 18 lakhs and other valuable assets he had in setting up a new store.

Hasan is a resident of Yakutpura and had the grocery store for six years. However, he decided to expand his business and shifted to a new commercial store space in Balapur.

On April 29, like any other regular day, he closed his shop at the day’s end and left for his house. At nearly 4:30 am the next morning, he received a call which gave him the shock of his life.

Passersby noticed smoke coming out of his shop and informed him about the mishap through his cell phone number displayed outside his shop.

Hasan then immediately rushed to his site to find that his shop was nearly destroyed. Fire engines were called to the site and the flames were doused.

Hasan then raised a complaint at the nearby police station following which an FIR was lodged and police after investigation revealed that a shock circuit was the reason behind the fire mishap.

Left indebted and shattered by the loss, Hasan tried reaching the state government officials for help.

For nearly 40 days now, Hasan has been roaming around to claim the chief minister’s relief fund, hoping that it would compensate for the loss to some extent as his shop was yet to be insured.

पटना में विपक्ष की एकता बैठक से पहले कांग्रेस नेता राहुल गांधी ने कहा की, हम सब एकसाथ मिलकर हम बीजेपी को हराने जा रहे हैं। कर्नाटक में हम लोगों ने बीजेपी को हराया है। उन्होंने दावा किया कि तेलगांना, मध्य प्रदेश, राजस्थान और छत्तीसगढ में कांग्रेस पार्टी की सरकार बनेगी।
देश में दो विचारधाराओं की लड़ाई चल रही है एक हमारी भारत जोड़ो की और एक तरफ भाजपा की भारत तोड़ो विचारधारा की। बीजेपी हिंदुस्तान को तोड़ने का काम कर रही है। नफरत और हिंसा फैलाने का काम कर रही है और कांग्रेस पार्टी जोड़ने का काम कर रही है और मोहब्बत फैलाने का काम करते हैं। नफरत को नफरत से नहीं काटा जा सकता है, नफरत को मोहब्बत से ही काटा जा सकता है।
नीतीश कुमार के बुलावे पर आज पटना में विपक्षी दलों का महाजुटान होने जा रहा हैं। राहुल गांधी बैठक में शामिल होने पटना पहुंच चुके हैं। कांग्रेस अध्यक्ष मल्लिकार्जुन खरगे भी इस बैठक में शामिल हो रहे हैं।
बैठक में शामिल होने से पहले राहुल गांधी गांधी पटना में कांग्रेस कार्यालय पर गए। यहां कार्यकर्ताओं को संबोधित करते हुए कहा, पूरा देश समझ गया है कि नरेंद्र मोदी और भाजपा का मतलब सिर्फ 2-3 लोगों को फायदा पहुंचाना है वहीं कांग्रेस का मतलब देश के गरीबों के साथ खड़े होना और उनके लिए काम करना है।
कांग्रेस अध्यक्ष मल्लिकार्जुन खरगे ने भी कांग्रेस कार्यालय पर कहा, इस कांग्रेस ऑफिस से जो भी नेता निकला वे देश के आजादी के लिए लड़ा है। हमें गर्व है कि देश के पहले राष्ट्रपति डॉ राजेंद्र प्रसाद जी इसी धरती से थे। अगर हम बिहार जीत गए तो सारे भारत में हम जीत जाएंगे।

The Saudi Transport General Authority (TGA) will introduce self-driving buses to assist pilgrims during this year’s Hajj season.

The buses are part of an initiative to provide innovative and environmental friendly transportation options for the millions of worshippers visiting the holy sites.

The buses utilize artificial intelligence, cameras, and sensors to operate within designated routes. By collecting and analyzing data during transit, the buses can make decisions to enhance the passenger experience and ensure safety.

According to the Saudi Transport Authority, each bus has an 11-seat capacity, can operate for 6 hours per charge, and has a top speed of 30 kilometers per hour.

The move aims to streamline the movement of pilgrims and evaluate the feasibility of utilizing these cutting-edge technologies in Hajj. The data and insights gathered will help set conditions for potential commercial operations in the coming years.

India has decided to join the Artemis Accords, which brings like-minded countries together on civil space exploration, and NASA and ISRO have agreed to a joint mission to the International Space Station in 2024, the White House said Thursday.

On space, we will be able to announce that India is signing the Artemis Accords, which advance a common vision for space exploration for the benefit of all humankind, a senior administration official said hours before the meeting between Prime Minister Narendra Modi and President Joe Biden in the Oval Office.

Grounded in the Outer Space Treaty of 1967 (OST), the Artemis Accords are a non-binding set of principles designed to guide civil space exploration and use in the 21st century. It is an American-led effort to return humans to the moon by 2025, with the ultimate goal of expanding space exploration to Mars and beyond.

The official said that NASA and the ISRO are developing a strategic framework for human spaceflight cooperation this year. In addition, NASA and ISRO have agreed to a joint mission to the International Space Station in the year 2024, said the official who spoke on condition of anonymity.

HP High Court has taken a serious note of the conduct of a contractor, whereby majority of the works, as awarded to him, have not been started and, if started, have not been completed. 

A Division Bench, comprising Justice Tarlok Singh Chauhan and Justice Virender Singh passed this order on the petition filed by Sanjeev Kumar Bhandari.

The petitioner Sanjeev Kumar Bhandari, a Government Contractor, approached High Court with claim that work for construction of Dosa-Ra-Tharu-Putlifald, Lower Brahmfald Jhared Galu, Chanouta road was awarded in his favour. 

But vide order dated 04.09.2021,  the Executive Engineer, HP PWD, Dharampur Division, District Mandi, re-invited the tender for aforesaid work. 

The petitioner prayed to quash the order regarding re-tendering of work in question and to direct respondents to award the tender work in his favour.

During the course of hearing the Court was informed at the Bar that the petitioner has been awarded as many as 66 contracts/works. 

The majority of the works awarded to him, have not been started and, if started, have not been completed.

Taking strict note, the Court has directed the petitioner to file an affidavit clearly setting out therein the timeline within which he would complete the works in question, which either have not been started or, if started, are in the mid-way. 

The fresh report of the status has been ordered to be filed in the matter on 13.07.2023.

The government has made significant amendments to the contentious bill amending Malta’s criminal provisions on abortion with the apparent intent of addressing the key concerns of those fearing it could legalise abortion by stealth: not least by amending the provision allowing the termination of pregnancy if a woman’s health in a grave danger.

The new bill presented on Friday now specify that Malta’s criminal provisions on abortion do not apply when a woman’s health is in “grave jeopardy which can lead to death,” a change that legalises the current situation faced by medical practitioners, and which alters the scope and wording of the original bill presented in Parliament.

The original wording had been a key concern for pro-life activists and others opposed to the legal provision of abortion, leading a group of academics to propose an amendment that removed references to “grave jeopardy” entirely.

Cocoa farms in Indonesia are leading the way in preserving biodiversity and protecting our planet's ecosystems. Through sustainable farming practices and conservation efforts, they are revolutionizing the chocolate industry while safeguarding the environment.

By implementing eco-friendly techniques, cocoa farmers prioritize the health of surrounding ecosystems. They create shade-grown cocoa plantations, allowing native trees and plants to flourish alongside cocoa trees, supporting a diverse range of wildlife.

Reforestation is a key focus, with trees planted to restore habitats and prevent deforestation. Forested areas preserve vital wildlife corridors and provide a home for endangered species.

Cocoa farms also prioritize organic farming methods, reducing synthetic pesticides and promoting natural pest control. This approach ensures the health of cocoa farmers, consumers, and ecological balance.

Indonesian cocoa farmers are not only making a positive impact on biodiversity but also empowering local communities. They provide fair wages and support social programs, enhancing education, healthcare, and infrastructure development in cocoa-growing regions.

As global demand for ethically sourced cocoa products grows, Indonesian cocoa farms inspire the chocolate industry worldwide. Together, we can indulge in delicious chocolate while preserving the planet's rich biodiversity.

Azizi developments will be building what they term as Dubai’s newest seven-star hotel. Aimed at completion by 2027, the skyscraper alongside being a seven-star property will also be  fifth tallest building in the world and the second tallest in Dubai.
“The seven-star hotel is a huge project which will change the skyline of Dubai,” said Azizi’s hospitality COO Michael Zager, reported Arabian Business’ sister publication, Hotelier Middle East.

The development is part of Azizi’s plan to invest up to AED60bn as it announces plans to build 50 luxury hotels in the city.

Azizi plans to add 20,000 new keys to Dubai’s hotel stock over the next five years which will be managed by its very own hospitality division.

Dubai developer to invest $16bn in 50 new hotels, plans 7-star property
Azizi has already acquired most of the necessary plots of land for its hotels and is planning to launch the construction before the end of 2023.

Mirwais Azizi, Founder and Chairman of Azizi Developments, said: “With the UAE’s Tourism Strategy 2031 aiming to leverage public-private partnerships and seeking to attract over AED100bn in new investment in the tourism sector, we have decided to make a major investment in the hospitality sector.

Pakistan International Airlines has completed the first phase of the Hajj operation, taking the last pilgrimage flight from Pakistan to Saudi Arabia Thursday night as more than two million are expected to perform Hajj this year.

The pre-Hajj operation culminated with the PIA flight operated from Karachi to Jeddah last night. About 61,467 pilgrims have flown to Saudi Arabia through 268 flights. Out of these, 41,000 pilgrims are performing Hajj on a government scheme and 19,600 are private pilgrims.

The PIA pre-Hajj flight operation started on May 21 and was completed on June 22.

Direct flights departed from Karachi, Islamabad, Lahore, Multan, Faisalabad, Sialkot, and Peshawar. From Sukkur, Rahim Yar Khan, and Quetta, pilgrims flew to Jeddah via Karachi Airport. The on-time departure ratio of PIA Hajj flights was 94%.

Out of 268 flights, 249 flights departed on time or shortly before time. During the entire Hajj operation, only 19 flights were delayed due to various reasons.

The PIA CEO congratulated the concerned teams for the high ratio of timely departures. The national flag carrier will start the post-Hajj operation on July 2 and it will continue till August 2.

BREAKING NEWS: Ugandan Border Town Prepares to Bury Victims of Rebel Massacre that Left 42 Dead, Mostly Students

A bereaved Ugandan border town on Sunday began burying the victims of a brutal attack on a school by suspected extremist rebels that left 42 people dead, most of them students, as security forces stepped up patrols along the frontier with volatile eastern Congo.

One of eight people wounded in Friday night’s attack, in which 38 students were killed, died overnight, said Selevest Mapoze, mayor of the town of Mpondwe-Lhubiriha.

“Most of the relatives have come to take their bodies” from the morgue, he said.

In addition to the 38 students, the victims include a school guard and three civilians. At least two of them, members of the same family, were buried Sunday.

The Institute of Nano Science and Technology in Mohali, an autonomous research institute under the department of science and technology, has developed a technology to test for sepsis in realtime, where the results will be available within a minute as compared to the minimum of 24 hours it currently takes -- a move that could help prevent the infection that is one of the factors behind millions of deaths in India every year.

“Rapid and early detection of sepsis biomarkers is essential and an immediate need to prevent significant casualties of ICU (intensive care unit) patients caused by an uncontrolled infection in the patient’s body. A highly sensitive and selective surface-enhanced Raman Spectroscopy (SERS) based detection protocol has been established to detect sepsis biomarkers,” said Rehan Khan from INST, one of the scientists behind the technology.

Sepsis is the body’s extreme response to an infection and happens when an existing infection triggers a chain reaction in the body, which if not recognised early and managed promptly can lead to septic shock, multiple organ failure and death.

A range of biomarkers are associated with sepsis, including fluid phase pattern recognition molecules (PRMs), cytokines, chemokines, damage-associated molecular patterns (DAMPs), non-coding RNAs, miRNAs, cell membrane receptors, cell proteins, metabolites, and soluble receptors.

The technology developed by scientists at INST through biomarkers, will be able to provide an accurate picture to healthcare providers on the severity of sepsis in patients to ensure timely intervention.

A 2022 study conducted by a team of scientists from India and Australia showed that more than half of the patients in intensive care units in India suffer from sepsis, stating that there was a sharp rise in such cases over the past decade. According to the study, researchers found sepsis in over 56% cases among 677 patients sampled from 35 ICUs all over the country. In about 45% of cases, the infection was caused by multi-drug resistant bacteria.

Dalam kesempatannya, Kapolresta Deli Serdang memaparkan jumlah barang bukti Narkotika yang akan dimusnahkan yakni Ganja seberat 172.986 gr, Shabu 19.386,93 gr dan Pil Extacy sebanyak 9.452.

“Dapat diasumsikan dengan jumlah barang bukti yang kami sebutkan, kita telah menyelamatkan generasi muda penerus bangsa kurang lebih 1.558.000 jiwa”pungkasnya.

Ketua FKUB Deli Serdang an. H. Waluyo dalam sambutannya turut mengapresiasi Polresta Deli Serdang atas kinerja selama ini terutama dalam memberantas Narkoba di wilkum Polresta Deli Serdang

On Wednesday, the UK prosecuted a paedophile, Mathew Smith, in a child pornography racket that has India links.

At least 969 cases pertaining to the online transmission of CSAM were registered by the National Crime Records Bureau (NCRB), but this is just the tip of the iceberg, officials pointed out at the first “National Conference on CSAM”, organised by the National Human Rights Commission (NHRC) on March 2-3. This number was 805 in 2021, 842 in 2020 and just 164 in 2019, according to NCRB.

The minutes of the meeting of the conference were released recently and have been reviewed by HT.

Speaking at the conference, NCRB director Vivek Gogia said: “The data pertaining to CSAM may not reflect the total number of cases”. He added there is an increasing trend in the number of cases reported owing to heightened awareness among law enforcement agencies (LEAs), expansion of digital technology and intervention by media and civil society.

Gogia added that India accessed United States’ NCMEC (National Center for Missing and Exploited Children) for data on CSAM, which are shared with the concerned states and UTs through the National Cybercrime Reporting Portal for further action.

Over 4 million cyber tipline reports have been shared with the concerned states/UTs for taking necessary action. Many of these reports are related to child sexual abuse material online.

OP Singh, chief executive officer of India Child Protection Fund and retired Indian Police Service (IPS) officer said, “There are three variables pertaining to sexual abuse of children -- anti-social trait in the offender, a sexual interest in children and situational factors such as access to children. The forms of online child sexual abuse include sextortion, grooming, and self-generated live streaming of CSAM. With the increase in the number of active internet users, the extent of the problem has become alarming”.

Perpetrators of online child sexual abuse and exploitation use social media, live streaming, and messaging apps, from Facebook to Instagram to Snapchat, to Tik Tok to Skype to Zoom, to target children.

As police were searching for a suspect wanted on drug possession, the hidden person’s location was given away after they suffered from a bout of loud flatulence.

“If you’ve got a felony warrant for your arrest, the cops are looking for you and you pass gas so loud it gives up your hiding spot, you’re definitely having a [poop emoji] day. #ItHappened,” the Clay County Sheriff’s Office posted to their Facebook page.

The department also posted images of police dogs, which they used as part of their search methods in a wooded area in Liberty, Missouri.

The city also got involved in the fart-joke fun.

On their Twitter account, they posted: “Thanks to [The Clay County Sheriff’s Office] for airing out a wanted person's dirty laundry and fanning the flames.”

The post continued: “The Liberty Police Department was surprised to see this incident slip out, which stinks for the arrestee. Fortunately, no one was injured during his arrest.”

“We’ve gotta give props to Liberty PD for using their senses to sniff him out!” said the sheriff’s department told local Fox 2 St Louis.

No name has been provided for the suspect and authorities have yet to release more information.

Police say no one was injured during the arrest.

[Source: Independent]

Dewan Pengawas Komisi Pemberantasan Korupsi (Dewas KPK) menduga rekening yang digunakan untuk menyalurkan atau menampung uang pungutan liar (pungli) di rumah tahanan (Rutan) KPK lebih dari satu. Dewas KPK sebelumnya telah mengungkapkan bahwa pungli di rutan KPK sebesar Rp 4 miliar menggunakan rekening pihak ketiga.

“Saya lupa tapi lebih dari satu rekening,” kata Anggota Dewas KPK, Syamsuddin Haris saat dihubungi Kompas.com, Jumat (23/6/2023). Syamsuddin lantas membenarkan pihaknya telah menerima hasil temuan Pusat Pelaporan dan Analisis Transaksi Keuangan (PPATK).

KPK memang bekerja sama dengan PPATK dalam mengusut dugaan pungli di tempat penahanan tersangka korupsi itu. Meski demikian, Syamsuddin mengaku Dewas belum mengetahui lebih lanjut apakah para oknum tersebut menggunakan rekening orang terdekat atau pengusaha.

“Dewas sendiri tidak tahu, makanya kita tunggu saja hasil penyelidikan KPK,” ujar Syamsuddin Haris.

Wakil Ketua KPK Nurul Ghufron sebelumnya mengungkapkan bahwa uang panas dugaan pungli di Rutan Kelas I Jakarta Timur Cabang KPK tidak langsung mengalir ke rekening oknum pegawai. Menurutnya, oknum pegawai KPK diduga menggunakan beberapa lapis transaksi untuk mengaburkan aliran dana tersebut.

“Sekilas saja bahwa dugaannya itu memang tidak langsung kepada rekening pegawai-pegawai yang diduga tersebut, memang diduga menggunakan layer-layer,” ujar Ghufron kepada wartawan, Kamis (22/6/2023).

ਯੂਟੀ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਦੇ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਨੇ ਡੀਜ਼ਲ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ CNG 'ਚ ਤਬਦੀਲ ਕਰਨ ਦਾ ਕੀਤਾ ਫੈਸਲਾ

ਚੰਡੀਗੜ੍ਹ : ਆਪਣਾ ਪੰਜਾਬ ਮੀਡੀਆ : ਯੂਟੀ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਦੇ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਨੇ ਚੰਡੀਗੜ੍ਹ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਅੰਡਰਟੇਕਿੰਗ ਸ਼ਹਿਰ ਦੀਆਂ ਡੀਜ਼ਲ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸੀਐਨਜੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਬਦਲਣ ਦਾ ਫੈਸਲਾ ਕੀਤਾ ਹੈ। ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸੀਐਨਜੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਤਬਦੀਲ ਕਰਨ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ ਸ਼ਹਿਰ ਦੀਆਂ ਜ਼ਿਆਦਾਤਰ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਸੀਐਨਜੀ ਅਤੇ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਹੋ ਜਾਣਗੀਆਂ। ਵਿਭਾਗ ਦਾ ਇਹ ਕਦਮ ਸ਼ਹਿਰ ਦੀ ਹਰਿਆਲੀ ਨੂੰ ਬਚਾਉਣ ਲਈ ਹੈ। ਇੱਕ ਅਧਿਕਾਰੀ ਨੇ ਦੱਸਿਆ ਕਿ ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਜੈਕਟ 'ਤੇ ਲਗਭਗ 35.31 ਕਰੋੜ ਰੁਪਏ ਦੀ ਲਾਗਤ ਆਉਣ ਦੀ ਸੰਭਾਵਨਾ ਹੈ, ਜਿਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਪੰਜ ਸਾਲਾਂ ਲਈ ਵਿਆਪਕ ਰੱਖ-ਰਖਾਵ ਵੀ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਹੈ। ਇਸ ਕੰਮ ਲਈ ਕੰਪਨੀ ਨੂੰ ਨਿਯੁਕਤ ਕਰਨ ਦਾ ਟੈਂਡਰ ਜਲਦੀ ਜਾਰੀ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ। ਦੱਸ ਦੇਈਏ ਕਿ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਨੇ ਇਸ ਸਾਲ 80 ਅਜਿਹੇ ਵਾਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਆਪਣੇ ਮੌਜੂਦਾ ਫਲੀਟ ਵਿੱਚ 100 ਹੋਰ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਕਰਨ ਦੀ ਯੋਜਨਾ ਬਣਾਈ ਹੈ। ਬੱਸਾਂ ਦੀ ਖਰੀਦ 2027-28 ਤੱਕ ਸਥਾਨਕ ਜਾਂ ਉਪਨਗਰੀ ਰੂਟਾਂ 'ਤੇ ਚੱਲਣ ਵਾਲੀਆਂ ਸੀਟੀਯੂ ਦੀਆਂ 258 ਡੀਜ਼ਲ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਦੇ ਪੂਰੇ ਫਲੀਟ ਨੂੰ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨਾਲ ਬਦਲਣ ਦੀ ਯੂਟੀ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਦੀ ਯੋਜਨਾ ਨੂੰ ਵੱਡਾ ਹੁਲਾਰਾ ਦੇਵੇਗੀ। ਇੱਕ ਅਧਿਕਾਰੀ ਨੇ ਕਿਹਾ ਕਿ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਨੇ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਦੇ 100 ਹੋਰ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਦੀ ਖਰੀਦ ਦੀ ਤਜਵੀਜ਼ ਨੂੰ ਮਨਜ਼ੂਰੀ ਦੇ ਦਿੱਤੀ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ ਇਹ ਇਸ ਸਾਲ ਸੜਕ 'ਤੇ ਆਉਣ ਦੀ ਸੰਭਾਵਨਾ ਹੈ।ਟ੍ਰਾਈਸਿਟੀ ਦੀਆਂ ਸੜਕਾਂ 'ਤੇ 80 ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਚੱਲ ਰਹੀਆਂ ਹਨ। ਪਿਛਲੇ 18 ਮਹੀਨਿਆਂ ਤੋਂ ਵੱਧ ਸਮੇਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ 70 ਲੱਖ ਤੋਂ ਵੱਧ ਯਾਤਰੀ ਸਫ਼ਰ ਕਰ ਚੁੱਕੇ ਹਨ।

 واشنگٹن: امریکی اخبار نے دعویٰ کیا ہے کہ سمندر کے پانی کے اندر ایک زوردار دھماکے کی آواز سنی گئی تھی جو ممکنہ طور پر آبدوز کے پھٹنے کی آواز تھی جس سے امریکی بحریہ کے اہلکاروں نے متعلقہ حکام کو فوری طور پر آگاہ بھی کردیا تھا۔ 
امریکی اخبار وال اسٹریٹ جرنل کی رپورٹ کے مطابق 111 سال قبل ڈوبنے والے عظیم جہاز ٹائی ٹینک کے ملبے کو دیکھنے کے لیے جانے والے سیاحوں کی آبدوز ٹائٹن اپنے سفر کے آغاز کے چند گھنٹوں بعد ہی دھماکے سے پھٹ گئی تھی۔
لاپتا آبدوز ٹائٹن میں موجود پاکستانی تاجر شہزادہ داؤد کون ہیں؟
وال اسٹریٹ جرنل نے امریکی بحریہ کے ایک سینئر اہلکار کا حوالہ دیتے ہوئے دعویٰ کیا کہ آبدوزوں کا سراغ لگانے کے لیے بنائے گئے خفیہ صوتی نظام کے ذریعے سمندر کےاندر ایک دھماکا سنا گیا تھا۔
لاپتا آبدوز کے نقائص پر5 سال قبل آواز اُٹھانے والے ڈائریکٹر کو نوکری سے نکال دیا گیا تھا
امریکی بحریہ کے اہلکار نے مزید بتایا کہ اعداد و شمار کا تجزیے سے لگتا ہے کہ یہ دھماکا عین اس وقت سنا گیا تھا جب آبدوز ٹائٹن کا رابطہ منقطع ہوا تھا اور مقام بھی وہی تھا جہاں آبدوز ٹائٹن کو اُس وقت ہونا چاہیے تھا۔
امریکی بحریہ کے اہلکار نے کہا کہ کیوں کہ اُس وقت تصدیق نہیں ہوسکی تھی کہ دھماکا اسی آبدوز کا ہے اس لیے ملبہ ملنے تک ریسکیو آپریشن جاری رکھا گیا۔
یاد رہے کہ گزشتہ روز امریکی کوسٹ گارڈ نے ٹائٹن آبدوز کا ملبہ سمندر کے نیچے 3,800 میٹر (12,400 فٹ) پر ملنے کی تصدیق کرتے ہوئے کہا تھا تھا کہ ملبے کے معائنے سے لگتا ہے کہ آبدوز کم دباؤ کے باعث پھٹ گئی تھی۔
 ٹائٹن آبدوز کمپنی نے مسافروں کی ہلاکت کی تصدیق کردی
آبدوز کی ملکیت رکھنے والی کمپنی اوشن گیٹ نے تمام مسافروں کی ہلاکت کی تصدیق کی تھی۔ یہ آبدوز 18 جون کو اپنے سفر پر روانہ ہوئی تھی۔

रायपुर, जनजागरुकता। कांग्रेस के बड़े पदाधिकारियों की गुरुवार को सीएम आवास में बैठक हुई। जहां पार्टी के बड़े नेता प्रदेश में हुई नई नियुक्तियों पर आपत्ति जताते हुए नाराज हुए। उसके बाद नियुक्ति के नए आदेश को रद्द कर दिया गया।
मामले के अनुसार प्रदेश कांग्रेस अध्यक्ष मोहन मरकाम के कुछ नेताओं को प्रभारी बनाए जाने के आदेश का मामला कांग्रेस की प्रदेश प्रभारी कुमारी सैलजा तक पहुंचा। उसके बाद उस आदेश को रद्द किया गया। वहीं कुमारी सैलजा ने केवल रवि घोष को प्रशासन और संगठन का प्रभारी बनाने के लिए तत्काल आदेश जारी करने कहा। 
इस बात को लेकर गुरुवार को सीएम हाउस में हुई बैठक में पार्टी के बड़े नेता इन नियुक्तियों पर नाराजगी जाहिर की। जानकारी अनुसार प्रदेश कांग्रेस अध्यक्ष मोहन मरकाम ने दो दिन पहले प्रदेश कांग्रेस के पदाधिकारियों को नया प्रभार सौंपने का आदेश जारी किया था।

SERANG – Dua puluh mahasiswa jurusan Teknik Mesin Universitas Negeri Sultan Ageng Tirtayasa (Untirta) yang tergabung dalam Himpunan Mahasiswa Mesin (HMM) Fakultas Teknik Untirta dan Lembaga Semi Otonom Kreativitas Mahasiswa Mesin Untirta (Kreammur) mempresentasikan sekaligus melakukan uji coba mobil hemat energi.

Mobil bernama Krakatoa EV.01 yang didesain selama 4 bulan dengan pendampingan dosen Teknik Mesin Untirta itu, akan dipertandingkan pada ajang internasional bergengsi, Shell Eco-Marathon Asia di Sirkuit Mandalika, Lombok, pada 4 sampai 9 Juli 2023 mendatang.

Mobil karya inovasi mahasiswa Untirta itu diuji coba di hadapan Rektor Untirta, Prof. Fatah Sulaiman dan Wakil Rektor Bidang Administrasi Umum, Perencanaan, Pengelolaan Keuangan, SDM dan Fasilitas, H. Kurnia Nugraha di Serang.

Pada ajang Shell Eco-Marathon Asia di Sirkuit Mandalika, Lombok, merupakan keikutsertaan perdana Untirta pada kompetisi tahunan yang berfokus pada inovasi kendaraan aman dengan efisiensi sumber energi dan jarak tempuh terjauh tersebut.

ਯੂਟੀ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਦੇ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਨੇ ਡੀਜ਼ਲ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ CNG 'ਚ ਤਬਦੀਲ ਕਰਨ ਦਾ ਕੀਤਾ ਫੈਸਲਾ

ਚੰਡੀਗੜ੍ਹ : ਆਪਣਾ ਪੰਜਾਬ ਮੀਡੀਆ : ਯੂਟੀ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਦੇ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਨੇ ਚੰਡੀਗੜ੍ਹ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਅੰਡਰਟੇਕਿੰਗ ਸ਼ਹਿਰ ਦੀਆਂ ਡੀਜ਼ਲ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸੀਐਨਜੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਬਦਲਣ ਦਾ ਫੈਸਲਾ ਕੀਤਾ ਹੈ। ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸੀਐਨਜੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਤਬਦੀਲ ਕਰਨ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ ਸ਼ਹਿਰ ਦੀਆਂ ਜ਼ਿਆਦਾਤਰ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਸੀਐਨਜੀ ਅਤੇ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਹੋ ਜਾਣਗੀਆਂ। ਵਿਭਾਗ ਦਾ ਇਹ ਕਦਮ ਸ਼ਹਿਰ ਦੀ ਹਰਿਆਲੀ ਨੂੰ ਬਚਾਉਣ ਲਈ ਹੈ। ਇੱਕ ਅਧਿਕਾਰੀ ਨੇ ਦੱਸਿਆ ਕਿ ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਜੈਕਟ 'ਤੇ ਲਗਭਗ 35.31 ਕਰੋੜ ਰੁਪਏ ਦੀ ਲਾਗਤ ਆਉਣ ਦੀ ਸੰਭਾਵਨਾ ਹੈ, ਜਿਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਪੰਜ ਸਾਲਾਂ ਲਈ ਵਿਆਪਕ ਰੱਖ-ਰਖਾਵ ਵੀ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਹੈ। ਇਸ ਕੰਮ ਲਈ ਕੰਪਨੀ ਨੂੰ ਨਿਯੁਕਤ ਕਰਨ ਦਾ ਟੈਂਡਰ ਜਲਦੀ ਜਾਰੀ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ। ਦੱਸ ਦੇਈਏ ਕਿ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਨੇ ਇਸ ਸਾਲ 80 ਅਜਿਹੇ ਵਾਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਆਪਣੇ ਮੌਜੂਦਾ ਫਲੀਟ ਵਿੱਚ 100 ਹੋਰ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਕਰਨ ਦੀ ਯੋਜਨਾ ਬਣਾਈ ਹੈ। ਬੱਸਾਂ ਦੀ ਖਰੀਦ 2027-28 ਤੱਕ ਸਥਾਨਕ ਜਾਂ ਉਪਨਗਰੀ ਰੂਟਾਂ 'ਤੇ ਚੱਲਣ ਵਾਲੀਆਂ ਸੀਟੀਯੂ ਦੀਆਂ 258 ਡੀਜ਼ਲ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਦੇ ਪੂਰੇ ਫਲੀਟ ਨੂੰ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਨਾਲ ਬਦਲਣ ਦੀ ਯੂਟੀ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਦੀ ਯੋਜਨਾ ਨੂੰ ਵੱਡਾ ਹੁਲਾਰਾ ਦੇਵੇਗੀ। ਇੱਕ ਅਧਿਕਾਰੀ ਨੇ ਕਿਹਾ ਕਿ ਪ੍ਰਸ਼ਾਸਨ ਨੇ ਟਰਾਂਸਪੋਰਟ ਵਿਭਾਗ ਦੇ 100 ਹੋਰ ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਦੀ ਖਰੀਦ ਦੀ ਤਜਵੀਜ਼ ਨੂੰ ਮਨਜ਼ੂਰੀ ਦੇ ਦਿੱਤੀ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ ਇਹ ਇਸ ਸਾਲ ਸੜਕ 'ਤੇ ਆਉਣ ਦੀ ਸੰਭਾਵਨਾ ਹੈ।ਟ੍ਰਾਈਸਿਟੀ ਦੀਆਂ ਸੜਕਾਂ 'ਤੇ 80 ਇਲੈਕਟ੍ਰਿਕ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਚੱਲ ਰਹੀਆਂ ਹਨ। ਪਿਛਲੇ 18 ਮਹੀਨਿਆਂ ਤੋਂ ਵੱਧ ਸਮੇਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਬੱਸਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ 70 ਲੱਖ ਤੋਂ ਵੱਧ ਯਾਤਰੀ ਸਫ਼ਰ ਕਰ ਚੁੱਕੇ ਹਨ।

Tim SAR berhasil menemukan lokasi pesawat milik Semuwa Air dengan nomor PK SMW yang dilaporkan hilang kontak dalam penerbangan Elelim-Poik, Kabupaten Yalimo, Papua Pegunungan. Namun, nasib penumpangnya belum diketahui.

Kadisops Basarnas Jayapura Marinus Ohoirat, Jumat (23/6), menjelaskan lokasi pesawat itu ditemukan pesawat helikopter milik PT. Intan Angkasa yang terbang dari Wamena sekitar pukul 15.30 WIT.

Lokasi pesawat berada di tengah hutan belantara antara Elelim-Poik dan saat ditemukan masih terlihat asap keluar dari badan pesawat. Helikopter tersebut menemukan lokasi sekitar pukul 16.08 WIT.

Canada's Online News Act, which requires platforms like Meta (formerly Facebook) and Google to negotiate commercial deals and pay news organizations for their content, has cleared the senate.

Meta has announced that news availability will be ended on Facebook and Instagram for all users in Canada before the bill takes effect, citing concerns over "fundamentally flawed legislation."

Google has called the bill "unworkable" in its current form and expressed a desire to work with the government to find a solution.

The federal government argues that the bill aims to enhance fairness in the Canadian digital news market and secure fair compensation for struggling news organizations.

Media industry groups have welcomed the bill's passage as a step toward market fairness, emphasizing the importance of supporting real journalism.

The Online News Act is expected to come into effect in Canada within six months, following discussions between the government and tech giants.

Former President Barack Obama recently gave an exclusive interview to CNN, where he expressed concerns about the state of democratic institutions in the United States and globally. While acknowledging that the federal indictment of his successor, Donald Trump, demonstrates the rule of law, he emphasized the need for ongoing efforts to sustain democracy. 
 
Obama highlighted the importance of protecting Ukraine's sovereignty as a crucial step toward safeguarding democracy in the long run. However, he also warned that democratic norms are being eroded, and economic and social inequalities pose challenges to maintaining healthy democracies. Obama stressed the need to reform existing democratic institutions, stating that democracy will prevail if people fight for it. He discussed various global democratic and political issues, including Trump's indictment, expressing that holding former presidents accountable upholds the principle that nobody is above the law. 
 
Obama expressed concerns about attempts to silence critics and intimidate the press, noting that these efforts are most prominent in the Republican Party but not unique to one party. Reflecting on his previous visit to Greece, where he celebrated the enduring power of American democracy, Obama acknowledged that concerns about democracy have intensified since then, with Trump's false claims and the Capitol insurrection exposing the fragility of the American system. He recognized the complexity of dealing with anti-democratic leaders as part of the American presidency and emphasized the importance of finding common interests while challenging troubling trends.

Two individuals have been apprehended by the Rapid Response Squad, a division of the Ekiti State Police Command, for engaging in the act of unlawfully extracting diesel from the generators employed to supply power to streetlights in the Ado Ekiti region of the state.

On Thursday, the State Police Public Relations Officer, Sunday Abutu, reported that two individuals identified as Danjuma and Idowu were apprehended on Wednesday by the RRS officers along NTA Road in Ado Ekiti. They were caught red-handed while attempting to flee with a 25-litre container filled with diesel, which was believed to have been unlawfully siphoned from the generator set.

Abutu said, “The suspects confessed during interrogation that they committed the crime. The suspects also confessed that they have been selling the stolen diesel to unsuspecting residents of Ado-Ekiti for some time. They will be arraigned in due course.”

Abutu urged residents to be security conscious and endeavour to report any untoward incident around them to security operatives for necessary action

Selanjutnya pelat nomor khusus RF diganti Z dengan diawali angka satu. Untuk mendapatnya pun tidak akan mudah karena ada mekanisme pengajuan serta diperketat dibanding sebelumnya.

🌊💔 Join us as we delve into the heart-wrenching story of OceanGate Inc's ill-fated mission to explore the depths of the Titanic shipwreck. In 2021, OceanGate offered a unique opportunity for 5 individuals to venture into the abyss on board the Titan submarine, with each ticket priced at $250,000.

At a staggering depth of 3,800 meters, the Titanic's resting place poses immense challenges, accessible to only a handful of the world's most advanced submarines. Unfortunately, Titan, an experimental submarine steered with a gaming controller, embarked on this treacherous journey without the required certifications.

Passengers faced grueling conditions throughout the 10-hour voyage, confined to sitting on the floor with minimal space and basic facilities. Tragically, contact was lost mid-way, leaving them stranded 4 km beneath the sea's surface. The submarine carried oxygen reserves lasting only 96 hours.

 Titan's Wreckage was found 1,600 away from Titanic's wreck. Due to massive pressure at that depth the submarine is assumed to have imploded. May they rest in peace. 🙏💙

A submersible that was exploring the wreckage of the RMS Titanic on the ocean floor suffered a “catastrophic implosion”, the US Coast Guard has confirmed, killing all five passengers on board.

The craft, known as Titan, lost contact with its surface vessel, the HMS Polar Prince, on Sunday morning during a diving expedition. An international search effort located debris near the Titanic site on Thursday morning and later identified it as the remains of Titan.

“This is an incredibly unforgiving environment down there on the sea floor and the debris is consistent with a catastrophic implosion of the vessel,” Rear Admiral John Mauger of the US Coast Guard said at a press briefing.

The cause of the implosion is still under investigation, but experts have speculated that it could have been triggered by a sudden change in pressure or a malfunction in the submersible’s systems.

OceanGate, the operator of the craft, confirmed the five people on board were its chief executive Stockton Rush, Pakistani businessman Shahzada Dawood and his son Suleman Dawood, British businessman Hamish Harding, and Paul-Henri Nargeolet, a French explorer — were all presumed dead.

🇵🇰 At least 209 Pakistanis were among those who lost their lives in the boat wreck off Greece last week, according to data shared by a Pakistani investigative agency.

Information provided to the Federal Investigation Agency (FIA) by families of missing passengers known to have boarded the boat that capsized off Greece’s coast suggests the death toll may be significantly higher than official figures.

Greek authorities say the number of victims stands at 82 and the number of survivors at 104, of whom 12 were Pakistanis.

Pakistan is yet to officially confirm how many of its citizens were on the boat but kick-started a DNA sampling effort to help Greece identify those who died. Officials gathered DNA samples from 201 families.

Hundreds of people of different nationalities, including Egyptians, Syrians and Palestinians, are believed to have been on board the vessel, in what is seen as the worst sea disaster in years for the region.

Puan Maharani mendorong pemerintah memastikan hewan kurban yang didistribusikan untuk perayaan Iduladha 2023 dalam kondisi sehat.

 Ia mengimbau pemerintah memperbanyak distribusi vaksin bagi hewan kurban agar terhindar dari virus lato-lato atau Lumpy Skin Disease (LSD). 

mengingat permintaan hewan kurban seperti sapi dan kambing tengah meningkat drastis menjelang perayaan Hari Raya Idul adha 2023. Sebagai salah satu daerah penyuplai hewan kurban, di Provinsi Banten diketahui terdapat 332 ekor hewan yang terinfeksi virus LSD. 

Puan meminta pemerintah memperbanyak pendistribusian vaksin ke peternakan agar dapat meminimalisir penyebaran virus pada hewan kurban. Dengan begitu, hewan kurban yang dijual lebih sehat saat dikonsumsi.

Four and a half years ago a tiger was poached in the Ratapani Sanctuary, an important location because of its source population of tigers. Now again a tiger died, but this time it seems that the cause of the tiger's death is a territorial conflict, although the exact reason will be determined once the post-mortem report becomes available, according to the Times of India.

It’s always tragic when a tiger dies, whether it is from fights or from poaching. In the case of Ratapani Sanctuary the chances of poaching are higher because of the lack of leadership. 

Despite the initial approval from the National Tiger Conservation Authority (NTCA) in 2008, Ratapani has yet to be officially declared as a tiger reserve. Already in January 2022, chief minister Shivraj Singh Chouhan gave his approval for Ratapani to be notified as a tiger reserve. But the necessary steps to implement this decision have not been taken - that’s one and a half years later. 

Why are they stalling?

Dubai’s Permanent Committee for Labour Affairs has introduced the “Saada” welfare initiative to bring joy to labourers during Eid Al-Adha. The program aims to uplift their spirits by offering them the chance to win valuable prizes, including brand new cars and Apple iPhones.

To ensure inclusivity, the Saada initiative will be implemented across various labourers accommodations in Al Quoz, Jebel Ali, and Muhaisnah. This ensures that all workers residing in Dubai can benefit from this gesture of goodwill.

Major General Obaid Muhair bin Suroor, Chairman of the Permanent Committee for Labour Affairs, is fully committed to including every labourer in the Saada program. Each labourer will receive coupon cards, and assistance will be available to facilitate the process. These cards will then be collected and entered into a draw.

The draw will span three days, with the announcement of the car prize winner scheduled for the final day of Eid Al-Adha. Alongside the exciting prize giveaways, the Saada initiative will also feature captivating entertainment, including traditional folklore and cultural performances, creating a joyful atmosphere for the workers.

The Saada initiative is made possible through the generous support of the Dubai Charity Association and Beit Al Khair Society. Esteemed organizations such as the Department of Economic Development (DED), Dubai Municipality, Islamic Affairs and Charitable Activities Department, Dubai Police, and the General Directorate of Residency and Foreign Affairs (GDRFA) have joined forces to ensure the success of this meaningful endeavor.

Abdullah Lashakri Muhammad, Secretary General of the committee, recognizes the invaluable role played by hardworking labourers in shaping the beauty of the UAE and its cities. Their dedication and sacrifices, leaving their families behind to work in the UAE, exemplify their indispensable contributions as the true backbone of Dubai.

O Tribunal Superior Eleitoral (TSE) suspendeu o julgamento de ação que pode tornar o ex-presidente Jair Bolsonaro (PL) inelegível por oito anos. A sessão será retomada na próxima terça-feira (27/06), às 19h, quando os votos começarão a ser proferidos.

A maior parte da sessão desta quinta (22/06) foi ocupada pela leitura do relatório do corregedor-geral eleitoral, Benedito Gonçalves. Ele será o primeiro a votar quando a sessão for retomada.

A sessão também teve as sustentações orais das partes e leitura do parecer do vice-procurador geral eleitoral, Paulo Gonet, que reforçou a defesa da inelegibilidade de Bolsonaro e da absolvição de Braga Netto, que foi candidato a vice na chapa de Bolsonaro nas eleições de 2022.

Para o Ministério Público, aceitar o discurso do ex-presidente contra as urnas seria “voltar-se contra a própria Constituição”.

A defesa apontou que o “bolsonarismo não está em julgamento”.

– Não está em julgamento, como quer se fazer crer, o bolsonarismo. Está em julgamento a reunião dos embaixadores, havida muito antes do início do período período eleitoral e das eleições – disse o advogado Tarcísio Vieira de Carvalho.

เหลืออีกหนึ่งปีเท่านั้นสำหรับศึกฟุตบอลยูโร 2024 รอบสุดท้าย ณ ประเทศเยอรมัน ล่าสุดสหพันธ์ฟุตบอลยุโรป หรือ ยูฟ่า ได้ทำการเปิดตัวมาสคอตประจำทัวร์นาเม้นต์ออกมาแล้ว แถมยังเปิดโอกาสให้ทุกคนสามารถช่วยกันตั้งชื่อให้กับมันอีกด้วย

In an exciting development, Ukraine has introduced new rules that allow businessmen from Pakistan and other countries to become e-residents. This means they can register as entrepreneurs in Ukraine, manage their businesses remotely, and pay taxes online.

The Ukrainian government aims to attract international entrepreneurs and create a hub for innovation. The e-residency program is currently being tested and will be fully launched soon. However, it’s important to note that e-residents will not be able to provide services to Ukrainian citizens and certain countries, like Russia and Belarus, are not eligible for e-residency.

The target audience for Ukrainian e-residency includes countries known for outsourcing IT services. The program has specific tax regulations, with e-residents paying a percentage of their income based on the type of business activity. The National Bank of Ukraine has also allowed e-residents to open bank accounts. The e-residency initiative has been in progress since 2019 as part of Ukraine’s efforts to offer a special status to foreign citizens.

All five people, including two Pakistanis, aboard a submersible missing near the wreck of the Titanic, died — likely in an instant — after their vessel suffered what the US Coast Guard said on Thursday was a “catastrophic implosion” in the ocean depths.

On board were British explorer Hamish Harding, French submarine expert Paul-Henri Nargeolet, Pakistani-British tycoon Shahzada Dawood and his son Suleman, and Stockton Rush, CEO of the sub’s operator OceanGate Expeditions.
The somber announcement ended a multinational search-and-rescue operation that captivated the world since the tiny tourist craft went missing in the North Atlantic four days ago.

Rear Admiral John Mauger told reporters in Boston that analysis showed debris found on the seafloor, 500 meters from the bow of the Titanic, was consistent with the implosion of the sub’s pressure chamber.

“On behalf of the United States Coast Guard and the entire unified command, I offer my deepest condolences to the families,” Mauger said. The Coast Guard announced earlier on Thursday that an underwater robot had discovered a “debris field” in the search area.

Sejumlah buruh Batam khususnya yang bekerja di kawasan industri Kabil Nongsa mengeluhkan rawan terjadinya kecelakaan saat jam pulang kerja.

Hal itu disampaikan perwakilan karyawan industri kepada Kapolsek Nongsa dalam Curhat Kamtibmas di Warung Pak Lis depan PT Sinergy Oil Kabil Nongsa, Jumat (23/6/2023) siang.

Dalam program Curhat Kamtibmas itu, anggota Polsek Nongsa bersama karyawan industri menggelar dialog seputar keluhan yang dialami buruh Batam.

Buruh Batam menilai, jika kepadatan arus lalu lintas saat jam pulang kerja tak dikawal maka dapat menimbulkan kecelakaan di Batam..

Sala satu karyawan industri yang juga masyarakat Nongsa, Novi mengaku kerap was-was melihat keamanan lalulintas dari pintu keluar perusahan yang rawan akan lakalantas.

“Mulai dari pintu keluar PT tempat kami kerja ini, sampai di simpang keluar PTK sangat rawan kecelakaan. Karena saat pekerja keluar dari perusahaan banyak juga kendaraan berat yang lewat,” ujarnya.

Mereka pun meminta ada patroli atau pun polisi lalu lintas yang hadir di jam pulang kerja karyawan

Ini bertujuan untuk meminimalisir terjadinya pencurian terhadap kendaraan yang sedang diparkir saat ditinggal bekerja.

Terakhir ia berpesan kepada seluruh masyarakat Nongsa, jika ada gangguan Kamtibmas ditengah masyarakat agar dapat berkoordinasi dengan Bhabinkamtibmas.

PENAMPAKAN PESAWAT SAM AIR YANG JATUH  DI PAPUA PEGUNUNGAN

Tim SAR tengah melakukan pencarian Pesawat Semua Aviasi Mandiri (SAM) Air hilang kontak di Kabupaten Yalimo, Papua Pegunungan, Jumat (23/6/2023).

Kepala Basarnas Marsekal Madya TNI Henri Alfiandi mengatakan, pihaknya telah menemukan lokasi yang diduga tempat erjatuhnya pesawat. Saat ini, Tim SAR dibantu dengan maskapai Susi Air tengah menuju ke lokasi.

"Tim SAR sudah menuju lokasi, Susi Air juga bantu lihat perkiraan tempat jatuhnya," tutur Henri saat dihubungi, Jumat (23/6/2023).

Henri memastikan, pihaknya telah melakukan aksi cepat untuk melakukan pencarian.

"Intinya Basarnas sudah aksi cepat dan ketahui posisi berdasarkan track penerbangannya," terang Henri.

Sebelumnya, pesawat Semuwa Aviasi Mandiri (SAM) Air hilang kontak di Kabupaten Yalimo, Papua Pegunungan, Jumat (23/6/2023). Pesawat gran caravan nomor penerbangan PK-SMW itu dilaporkan hilang kontak saat terbang dari Distrik Elelim ke Distrik Poik. 

Kepala Unit Penyelenggara Bandar Udara (UPBU) Elelim, Genos Imanuel, mengatakan pesawat hilang kontak sekitar pukul 10.00 WIT. Pesawat itu membawa empat penumpang.

"Memang benar pesawat yang membawa empat penumpang hilang kontak sejak pukul 10.00 WIT," kata Genos, Jumat (23/6/2023). GAL

Мбаппе перейдёт в «Реал» в летнее трансферное окно

Трансфер нападающего сборной Франции по футболу Килиана Мбаппе из «ПСЖ» в «Реал» всё-таки осуществится в летнее трансферное окно.

По информации инсайдеров «ПСЖ» из PSG Community, президент «Реала» Флорентино Перес договорился с руководством парижского клуба о трансфере 24-летнего Мбаппе за €200 млн. Еще €50 млн в виде бонусов «ПСЖ» получит в том случае, если Килиан выиграет «Золотой мяч».

Однако по данным COPЕ, «Реал» не готов тратить €250 млн на покупку Мбаппе. Прежде El Chiringuito заявляли, что мадридский клуб может отдать за трансфер форварда €120 млн.

Несмотря на заявления самого игрока, что он готов остаться и провести ещё один год в Париже, руководство «ПСЖ» заняло твёрдую позицию: Мбаппе или продлевает истекающий следующим летом контракт, или уходит. Разочарованный действиями клуба на трансферном рынке Килиан считает, что проект «ПСЖ» «ходит по кругу» и что пора искать новый вызов в своей карьере.

Мбаппе выступает за ПСЖ с 2018 года, в составе команды он стал пятикратным чемпионом Франции и трехкратным обладателем Кубка страны. Со сборной Франции форвард выиграл чемпионат мира 2018 года и завоевал серебро в 2022-м.

Even as mangoes are hugely in demand in markets across Gujarat, farmers of Kutch have been forced to dump tonnes of mangoes along the borders of their orchards due to the damage by Cyclone Biparjoy.

“The gusty winds of the cyclone caused massive damage. There are no takers for these mangoes. So, we are forced to dump them in the open areas near our orchards,” Ashok, a mango orchard owner from Sukhpar Roha village in Nakhatrana taluka of Kutch, told The Indian Express. He had to dump a massive quantity on Thursday.

Similar scenes are being witnessed in Anjar, Bhuj, Mandvi, and Mundra talukas, which along with Nakhtrana, form the main mango belt of Kutch.

“As these mangoes were whipped to the ground by gusty winds, they were either damaged or they started rotting. Rain and humid weather meant the rotting was rapid,” Nandkishor Jadeja, owner of an 18-acre mango orchard in Khedoi village in Anjar taluka of Kutch said, adding he dumped three-tractor-trolley-loads of mangoes near his orchard on Thursday.

As per the latest state government data, Kutch has horticulture crops across 57,735 hectares. Of that, mango orchards account for 10,960 hectares (ha) and are the third biggest horticulture crop of Kutch after pomegranate (19,325 ha) and date palms (19,111 ha).

The mango cultivation in Kutch is the fourth highest in the state after Valsad (37344 ha), Navsari (33855 ha), and Gir Somnath (14301 ha), and almost seven per cent of the state’s total mango orchards area of 1.66 lakh ha.  However, horticulture crops like fresh dates and mangoes suffered a large-scale damage as the district witnessed winds gusting up to 120 km per hour and torrential rains as Cyclone Biparjoy made landfall at Jakhau port in Abdasa taluka of Kutch on June 15.

“The harvest was at its peak when the cyclone hit. There is no point in taking damaged and rotting mangoes to market. Instead, we are asking people to take whatever they want from orchards and dumping the rest in the open for livestock to feed on,” Jadeja further said.

Banyaknya pengakses membuat laman PPDB Jatim 2023 sempat sulit diakses pada Jumat pagi (23/6/2023). Akibatnya, calon siswa SMA/SMK sempat tidak bisa melakukan pendaftaran.

Alvian Kepala Teknis Penerimaan Peserta Didik Baru (PPDB) SMA/SMK Jawa Timur 2023 mengatakan, sistem PPDB Jatim 2023 baik-baik saja, hanya server-nya yang penuh.

“Kita konfirmasikan bahwa saat ini sistem kami baik-baik saja, tidak sedang down,” kata Alvian kepada Radio Suara Surabaya, Jumat (23/6/2023).

Alvian menyambung bahwa alasan laman PPDB Jatim 2023 “down” karena banyaknya pengakses yang terdiri dari calon siswa dan orang tuanya juga. Calon pendaftar SMA/SMK itu sendiri tidak dibatasi hanya di Jawa Timur, melainkan dari seluruh Indonesia. Jumlah antrean juga bertambah karena menurut pengamatan Alvian, siswa cenderung melakukan refresh page sehingga jumlah antrean bertambah.

“Pendaftar dari luar Jawa Timur di tahap satu ini kan banyak, seperti jalur pindah tugas itu kan juga banyak,” jelas Alvian.

Dalam mengatasi ini, Alvian bersama tim Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember (ITS) bekerjasama untuk meningkatkan kapasitas server PPDB Jatim 2023 menjadi empat kali lipat dari angka awal.

“Pengguna sudah kami asumsikan dua kali lipat dari awal. Kami asumsikan 2 kali lipat dari total 575.108 siswa kami asumsikan 600 ribu, kemudian kami kalikan 2 jadi 1,2 juta. Ternyata hari ini 1,2 juta pengguna masih terdapat antrean. Oleh karena itu kami tingkatkan empat kali lipat. Jadi 2,5 juta kuota akses,” ujarnya.

Untuk teknis pengecekan sendiri, sambung Alvian, laman PPDB harus memverifikasi nomor PIN, NISN, dan tanggal lahir sesuai KK pendaftar. Verifikasi tiga data tersebut membutuhkan waktu 2-3 detik. Setelah itu laman baru bisa menampilkan informasi terkait penerimaan siswa itu.

“Kami sarankan juga akses internet dari posisi masyarakat dari wifi, sinyal data, dan hp-nya mohon dipastikan, karena itu juga menambah lama (loading, red) munculnya di handphone atau gadget masyarakat,” ungkapnya.

માનવ સેવા ચેરીટેબલ ટ્રસ્ટ ભાવનગર દ્વારા આજે શિહોર તાલુકાની શ્રી ધ્રુપકા પ્રાથમિક શાળામાં ધોરણ 3 અને 4ના બાળકોને 2 અને 5 થી 8ના બાળકોને 5  ફુલ્સકેપ ચોપડા અને પેન એમ કુલ 1500 જેટલા ચોપડા આપવામાં આવ્યા તથા આગળ અભ્યાસ માટે પ્રોત્સાહિત કરવામાં આવ્યા. 
માનવ સેવા ચેરીટેબલ ટ્રસ્ટ દ્વારા  દર વર્ષે ભાવનગર જિલ્લામાં જરૂરિયાત મંદ એવા 4500 થી વધુ બાળકોને ફુલ્સકેપ ચોપડાનું વિતરણ કરવામાં આવે છે. અને અન્ય સેવાકીય પ્રવૃતિઓ કરવામાં આવે છે.
ટ્રસ્ટના પ્રમુખ જયેશભાઈ શાહ દ્વારા બાળકોને આગળ અભ્યાસ માટે માર્ગદર્શન આપવામાં આવ્યું હતું સાથે હરેશભાઈ, મહિપાલસિંહ ગોહિલ, યાદવભાઈ અને પિંકીબેન દ્વારા પણ બાળકોને આગળ અભ્યાસ માટે પ્રેરણા આપવામાં આવી હતી.
શાળાના શિક્ષક શ્રી મહિપાલસિંહ ગોહિલના માર્ગદર્શનથી સતત સાત વર્ષથી શાળાના બાળકોને ટ્રસ્ટ દ્વારા ચોપડા આપવામાં આવે છે.
આ તકે શાળા પરિવાર દ્વારા ટ્રસ્ટના તમામ સભ્યોને  પુસ્તક આપી આવકારવામાં આવ્યા હતા.
કાર્યક્રમના અંતે વૃક્ષારોપણ કરવામાં આવ્યું હતું.
આ તકે શાળા પરિવાર માનવસેવા ચેરીટેબલ ટ્રસ્ટ અને શાળાના શિક્ષક મહિપાલસિંહ ગોહિલનો ખુબ ખુબ આભાર વ્યક્ત કરે છે.

BeInCrypto looks at five altcoins that increased the most in this week’s crypto market, specifically from June 16 to 23.

The term altcoin refers to cryptocurrencies other than Bitcoin (BTC). These bullish altcoins have stolen the crypto news and cryptocurrency market spotlight this week as the biggest gainers:

Pepe (PEPE) price increased by 71.44%
Stacks (STX) price increased by 46.11%
Conflux (CFX) price increased by 40.13%
Bitcoin Cash (BCH) price increased by 35.80%
WOO Network (WOO) price increased by 25.01%
Pepe (PEPE) Price Leads Bullish Altcoin Gainers
The PEPE price had fallen under a descending resistance line since May 11. The drop led to a low of $0.0000008 on June 13. However, the price has increased since and cleared the descending resistance line on June 21. This is a sign that the correction has ended.

After the breakout, the price reached a high of $0.0000015. PEPE is attempting to clear the 0.5 Fib retracement resistance at $0.0000015.

Pepe (PEPE) Price DecreasePEPE/USDT Six-Hour Chart. Source: TradingView
If it is successful, PEPE could move to the next resistance at $0.0000021. However, a drop that validates the resistance line at $0.0000011 will be expected if it gets rejected.

Stacks (STX) Price Bounces After Drop
The STX price fell sharply after a high of $1.31 on March 20. The decrease was swift, leading to a low of $0.44 on June 10. The price bounced afterward and has increased since. The increase caused it to reclaim and validate the $0.55 area as support. On June 22, STX reached a high of $0.88.

The wave count supports the continuing increase. Since November 2022, the STX price completed a five-wave increase. Then, the ensuing 82-day drop resembles a completed correction.

If so, the STX price has now begun a new upward movement that will take it to at least $1.40.

पंजाब सरकार ने अतिरिक्त धन राशि जुटाने के लिए एक नया पैंतरा निकाला है। सरकार ने पेंशनर्स की मासिक पेंशन पर 200 रुपए डेवलपमेंट टैक्स लगा दिया है। जिसको लेकर अब सरकार विपक्ष के निशाने पर आ गई है। वरिष्ठ कांग्रेस नेता और पूर्व कांग्रेस प्रदेश अध्यक्ष नवजोत सिंह सिद्धू ने ट्वीट के जरिए सीएम मान पर निशाना साधते हुए लिखा है कि तो भीख का कटोरा बाहर है, राज्य के लिए कोई आय नहीं। राजकोष व्यक्तियों द्वारा जेब में डाला जा रहा है।
सिद्धू ने आगे लिखा कि बेताब उधार, अप्रत्यक्ष कर और अब स्पष्ट प्रत्यक्ष कर। स्पष्ट रूप से पंजाब सरकार की वित्तीय स्थिति को "गंभीर स्थिति" में दर्शाता है। पंजाब में पेंशनभोगियों पर सीएम द्वारा 200 रुपये विकास कर भगवंत मान यह राज्य के लोगों पर पैसों का एक और हमला है। सत्ता हासिल करने के उद्देश्य से किए गए आत्मकेंद्रित वादे मतदाताओं पर कर लगाकर पूरे किए जा रहे हैं, जबकि माफिया सत्ता में बैठे लोगों को कमीशन देकर खनन, शराब, भूमि और परिवहन के माध्यम से पंजाब के खजाने का राजस्व निकालना जारी रखते हैं। बकरे की मां कब तक खैर मनाएगी? 
पंजाब के लोगों को फ्री सुविधाएं देने के बाद अब आम आदमी पार्टी की सरकार अपनी आमदनी बढ़ाने के लिए टैक्स वसूलने की तैयारी में है। अब 22 जून से पेंशनर्स की मासिक पेंशन पर 200 रुपए डेवलपमेंट टैक्स काटा जाएगा। गुरुवार को पंजाब वित्त विभाग की तरफ से ये फैसला लिया गया है। पंजाब में करीब 3.50 लाख पेंशनर्स है जिनसे सरकार को हर साल करीब 84 करोड़ रुपए की आय होगी। हर महीने के हिसाब से अगर देखा जाए तो सरकार को 7 करोड़ रुपए डेवलपमेंट टैक्स के तौर पर मिलेगे। 2023-24 के बजट में डेवलपमेंट टैक्स से 300 करोड़ रुपए हासिल करने का लक्ष्य रखा गया था। पेंशनर्स से डेवलपमेंट टैक्स की वसूली से सरकार अपने लक्ष्य से आगे निकल जाएगी।
पेंशनर्स की मासिक पेंशन पर 200 रुपए डेवलपमेंट टैक्स लगाने को लेकर अब पंजाब पेंशनर्स एसोसिएशन भी सरकार के विरोध में उतर चुका है। पेंशनर्स एसोसिएशन के महासचिव सुरिंदर राम का कहना है कि 24 और 25 जून को पूरे पंजाब में मंत्री और विधायकों के घरों का घेराव किया जाएगा और सरकार के आदेश की प्रतियां जलाई जाएगी।

തി​രു​വ​ന​ന്ത​പു​രം: മൃ​ഗ​ശാ​ല​യി​ൽ നി​ന്നും ചാ​ടി​പ്പോ​യ ഹ​നു​മാ​ൻ കു​ര​ങ്ങി​നെ മ​ര​ത്തി​ന്‍റെ മു​ക​ളി​ൽ നി​ന്നും താ​ഴെ​യി​റ​ക്കാ​നു​ള്ള അ​നു​ന​യ ശ്ര​മ​ങ്ങ​ൾ തു​ട​ർ​ന്ന് മൃ​ഗ​ശാ​ല അ​ധി​കൃ​ത​ർ. മ​സ്ക്ക​റ്റ് ഹോ​ട്ട​ലി​ന് സ​മീ​പ​ത്തെ മ​ര​ത്തി​ന് മു​ക​ളി​ലാ​ണ് ക​ഴി​ഞ്ഞ ര​ണ്ട് ദി​വ​സ​മാ​യി കു​ര​ങ്ങ് ക​ഴി​യു​ന്ന​ത്.

കു​ര​ങ്ങ് ഓ​രോ മ​ര​ത്തി​ൽ നി​ന്നും വേ​റൊ​രു മ​ര​ത്തി​ലേ​ക്ക് ചാ​ടി​പ്പോ​യി​ക്കൊ​ണ്ടി​രി​ക്കു​ക​യാ​യി​രു​ന്നു. ബു​ധ​നാ​ഴ്ച മു​ത​ലാ​ണ് മ​സ്ക്ക​റ്റ് ഹോ​ട്ട​ലി​ന് സ​മീ​പ​ത്തെ മ​ര​ത്തി​ന് മു​ക​ളി​ൽ ഇ​രി​പ്പു​റ​പ്പി​ച്ച​ത്.

The aromatic rice known as joha, which is grown in India's northeast, is useful for managing diabetes since it lowers blood sugar levels and delays the start of the disease.According to conventional wisdom, those who eat Joha rice have lower rates of diabetes and cardiovascular ailments.
The nutritional benefits of flavorful Joha rice were investigated by researchers at the Institute of Advanced Study in Science and Technology (IASST), a separate institute within the Department of Science and Technology. In their study, Rajlakshmi Devi and Paramita Choudhury examined the nutritional benefits of aromatic Joha rice.They identified two unsaturated fatty acids, linoleic acid (omega-6) and linolenic acid (omega-3), using in vitro laboratory investigation. These necessary fatty acids, which the human body lacks the ability to manufacture, can support a number of physiological functions. Numerous metabolic illnesses, including diabetes, cardiovascular disease, and cancer, can be prevented by omega-3 fatty acids.Joha rice also has an abundance of flavonoids, phenolics, and antioxidants. 
Additionally, the researchers discovered that when compared to the widely consumed non-scented version, scented Joha rice has a more balanced ratio of omega-6 to omega-3. Humans require about one omega-6 to one omega-3 essential fatty acid the same amount of EFA ratio in order to sustain a healthy diet. They also created rice bran oil, a patented product that they say is useful in the management of diabetes, using Joha rice.

पटना में आज विपक्षी एकता की बैठक मुख्यमंत्री नीतीश कुमार की अगुवाई में यह कार्यक्रम हो रहा है। सभी विपक्षी पार्टियों का एक ही लक्ष्य है बीजेपी को सत्ता से बाहर करना। बिहार कांग्रेस के प्रदेश अध्यक्ष अखिलेश प्रसाद सिंह ने बैठक से पहले बड़ा बयान देते हुए कहा है कि इस बार विपक्ष लड़ता है तो 2024 के लोकसभा चुनाव में बीजेपी 100 सीटों के अंदर सिमट कर रह जाएगी।

अखिलेश प्रसाद सिंह ने कहा कि देश की सभी विपक्षी पार्टियां एकजुट होकर आज पटना पहुंच रही हैं। निश्चित तौर पर हम लोग कामयाब होंगे। बिहार में तो BJP का पूरी तरह सफाया हो जाएगा क्योंकि BJP की ताकत नीतीश कुमार की बदौलत थी और अब नीतीश कुमार BJP से हट गए हैं तो BJP बिहार से खत्म हो जाएगी। लोकसभा के चुनाव में पूरे देश में बीजेपी को 100 सीट से भी कम आएगी।
अखिलेश बोले- बीजेपी की सरकार से ऊब चुकी है जनता
अखिलेश सिंह ने कहा कि RSS के नेतृत्व वाली बीजेपी की सरकार से जनता ऊब चुकी है और इसी को लेकर सभी विपक्ष एकजुट होना चाह रहे हैं। उन्होंने कहा बिहार पहले से भी परिवर्तन करता रहा है। एक बार फिर मोदी सरकार के खिलाफ सबकी एकजुट हुई है। बिहार से परिवर्तन शुरू किया जाएगा।उन्होंने कहा कि यह बात सही है कि पश्चिम बंगाल, दिल्ली या पंजाब में हमारी लड़ाई ममता बनर्जी और अरविंद केजरीवाल से है लेकिन उसी को लेकर आज हम लोग बात करेंगे। सभी मुद्दों पर बात होगी, लेकिन लक्ष्य एक ही रहेगा कि बीजेपी का देश से सफाया करना है।

प्रधानमंत्री पद का उम्मीदवार कौन होगा इस सवाल पर कहा कि 2004 में पहले तय नहीं किया गया था कि कौन प्रधानमंत्री होंगे। मनमोहन सिंह के बारे में किसी ने सोचा नहीं था और उनको प्रधानमंत्री बनाया गया था। विपक्षी पार्टियों में लगभग 10 से 11 लोग ऐसे हैं जो नरेंद्र मोदी से बढ़िया काम कर सकते हैं, इसलिए प्रधानमंत्री कौन बनेगा यह कोई मुद्दे की बात नहीं है।

Menjelang idul adha, Cici Gabriella bersigap menjadi sales promotion girl (SPG) hewan kurban (sapi) di Kandang Sapi Widistia, Surabaya. Meski tidak setiap hari berhasil menjual sapi, ia tetap bersyukur.⁠
⁠
Saat ditanya apa sesungguhnya cita-cita Cici, ia bilang ingin jadi peternak sapi yang sukses. Bergaul dengan 80-an sapi sudah jadi hal biasa untuknya. Pernah suatu waktu ia hampir diseruduk sapi.⁠
⁠
Ide SPG ini berasal dari Mad Yudi, Kepala Kandang Sapi Widistia. Mad menuturkan, penjualan sapinya meningkat terus. Tahun 2022 kemarin, sapinya laku sebanyak 300 ekor.⁠

FAKTUAL-INDONESIA : Kasus dugaan perselingkuhan artis Syahnaz Sadiqah dengan Rendy Kjaernett makin viral. Adalah Lady Nayoan istri dari Rendy yang menyebarkan kabar perselingkuhan itu melalui akun Instagramnya ke publik.

Bukan tanpa berpikir matang, Lady Nayoan sudah putuskan akan bercerai dari Rendy karena dirinya merasa tersakiti diselingkuhi.

Setelah menggelontorkan bukti-bukti tersebut, Lady pun mengaku sudah siap untuk bercerai dengan Rendy.

“Dari awal aku (bikin) keputusan untuk posting, aku sudah bulat mau cerai,” ujar Lady Nayoan dalam podcast bersama Richard Lee seperti dilihat detikcom pada Kamis (22/6).

KLATEN - Kepolisian Resor Klaten, Jawa Tengah mengungkap kasus pembunuhan disertai mutilasi dengan korban seorang perempuan berinisial R, 56 tahun, yang tercatat sebagai warga Bandung, Jawa Barat. Pembunuhan terjadi di sebuah rumah di Desa Nangsri, Kecamatan Manisrenggo, Kabupaten Klaten, Kamis, 22 Juni 2023. 

Tak sampai 24 jam, polisi berhasil membekuk pelaku berinisial T, warga Desa Sambirejo, Kecamatan Selomerto, Kabupaten Wonosobo. T tak lain merupakan teman korban, bahkan tinggal satu rumah dengan korban. 

Kapolres Klaten Ajun Komisaris Besar Warsono mengemukakan kasus pembunuhan T terhadap R dilatarbelakangi motif sakit hati dan dendam pelaku terhadap korban. Warsono mengungkapkan berdasarkan pengakuan tersangka, korban pernah menuduhnya mencuri uang miliknya senilai Rp 20 ribu. 

"Jadi, antara korban dan pelaku ini sebenarnya merupakan teman yang tinggal dalam satu rumah. Pelaku memang membantu pekerjaan korban. Sekitar dua pekan lalu pelaku ini dituduh mengambil uang milik korban. Karena tidak merasa mengambil sehingga pelaku jengkel dan menaruh dendam terhadap korban," ujar Warsono ketika menggelar konferensi pers di Mapolres Klaten.

SUDAH menjadi rahasia umum berbagai macam korupsi terjadi di lingkungan sekolah. Terutama setelah dilaksanakannya masa penerimaan siswa baru. Modus pembayaran rutin pada koperasi sekolah ini berpotensi menjadi ladang para guru dan petinggi sekolah meraih keuntungan untuk dirinya sendiri.

Landasan pokok berdirinya koperasi didasarkan pada UUD 1945 Pasal 33 Ayat 1. Kemudian peraturan koperasi diperinci dan tertuang dalam Undang-Undang Nomor 25 Tahun 1992. Dalam kepengurusannya koperasi sekolah berada di bawah bimbingan kepala sekolah serta guru-guru yang dibantu oleh para siswa yang tergabung menjadi anggota koperasi sekolah. 

Namun Dalampelaksanaannya pembayaran uang simpanan pokok ini tidak hanya berlaku pada siswa yang ingin bergabung menjadi anggota koperasi, melainkan hampir seluruh siswa diwajibkan membayar iuran ini.

Jumlah nominal yang dibayarkan memang tidak besar, berkisar di harga 10 ribu hingga yang paling mahal 30 ribu rupiah. Namun, jika dikalikan dengan rombongan belajar yang diterima dalam sekolah tersebut, nominal yang didapatkan bisa mencapai puluhan hingga ratusan juta rupiah.

Asumsi pemasukan dana koperasi hingga puluhan juta dari simpanan siswa dapat diperoleh dari hasil perkalian dana yang dibayarkan dengan rombongan belajar setiap angkatan (kelas 7, kelas 8, dan kelas 9). Simpanan pokok ini juga wajib dibayarkan siswa per bulannya.

Petugas kebersihan rumah sakit Meghla Akhtar (25) dan resepsionis Yasmin Akhtar (21) pergi untuk membuat video TikTok di atap gedung pada Selasa sekitar pukul 2 siang. Saat itu, kedua remaja putri itu terluka akibat sambaran petir. Kemudian, pihak rumah sakit langsung membawa kedua orang tersebut ke RS Shariatpur Sadar.

Five months after a stillborn baby was found in a toilet at a city hospital, police have arrested five persons, including the child’s parents, in connection with the incident. Police said apart from the infant’s parents, the woman’s sister and friends of her partner are among those arrested. The woman’s partner works as a delivery executive for an e-commerce platform.

DCP (Rohini) GS Sidhu said, “A PCR call was made at 12.30-1 am on January 22 after a person went to the hospital’s washroom and found the body in the toilet. The baby was stillborn… We were told that a pregnant woman had come to the hospital with four attendants but left without consulting the doctor. A case under IPC section 318 (concealment of birth by secret disposal of dead body) was registered.”

Police said the woman found out she was pregnant much later and she and her partner tried to allegedly terminate the pregnancy by taking pills. But she fell sick, said police. “… She had severe cramps and was rushed to the hospital by her sister, partner and his friends,” said an officer.

On January 21, the woman was admitted to the hospital around 9.30 pm. Police said initially, they had no details of the woman and her attendants.

During investigation, CCTVs from the hospital, nearby markets and areas were checked but the faces of the suspects were not “visible”, said police.

“The investigation team analysed around 250 CCTVs from the area. After a long search, one of the suspects was seen near a medical store (in the footage). The store owner was examined and he told us the suspect purchased medicine and paid for it online. On the basis of details of online transactions, the accused persons were identified and all of them were arrested,” said the DCP.

All Passengers on Titanic Submersible Confirmed Dead 

OceanGate, the diving company responsible for the Titanic tour, has confirmed that all five passengers aboard the submersible are dead. This was confirmed after a massive search by the US Coast Guard.

The Titanic Submersible went missing on Sunday, after it set out to on an expedition to see the wreck of the Titanic at the bottom of the North Atlantic Ocean, nearly 13, 000 feet below land. The expedition was priced at $250,000 per person.

Contact with the vessel was lost about one hour and 45 minutes into its descent. After extensive search, the tail cone of the Titan was found on the sea floor, about 1,600 feet away from the bow of the Titani and other debris nearby.

According to Rear Adm John Mauger of the US Coast Guard, the five passengers on board died what was believed to be a “catastrophic implosion”, based on the pattern of debris found.

Aboard the vessel was British Billionaire businessman Hamish Harding, Pakistani father and son, Shahzada and Suleman Dawood. OceanGate CEO Stockton Rush, and French Navy Diver Paul-Henry Nargeolet.

Green Diamond: PM Modi એ USની ફર્સ્ટ લેડીને ભેટમાં આપેલો ગ્રીન ડાયમંડ શું છે ??

What is Green Diamond: આ વર્ષે બજેટ ભાષણમાં નાણામંત્રી નિર્મલા સીતારમણે કહ્યું હતું કે દેશની IIT ને લેબમાં હીરા બનાવવાની જવાબદારી સોંપવામાં આવશે. આ માટે IITને ગ્રાન્ટ આપવામાં આવશે. ભારતને તેનું મેન્યુફેક્ચરિંગ હબ બનાવવાની તૈયારી ચાલી રહી છે.

લેબમાં બનેલો ડાયમંડ કેટલો ખાસ છે, 5 મોટી વાત કેવી રીતે અલગ: સામાન્ય રીતે હીરાની રચના જમીનમાં કેટલાક કિલોમીટરની ઊંડાઈએ થાય છે, પરંતુ પ્રયોગશાળામાં બનાવવામાં આવેલા હીરા અને સામાન્ય હીરા વચ્ચે તફાવત કરવો મુશ્કેલ છે. આ જ કારણ છે કે તેને આર્ટિફિશિયલ ડાયમંડ કહેવામાં આવે છે. લેબમાં હીરા બનાવવા માટે લગભગ 20 થી 30 દિવસનો સમય લાગે છે.

તેથી જ તેને ઇકો-ફ્રેન્ડલી ડાયમંડ કહેવામાં આવે છે: માઇક્રોસ્કોપ વિના સામાન્ય અને લેબ-નિર્મિત હીરા વચ્ચે તફાવત કરવો મુશ્કેલ છે. હાલમાં દેશમાં આવા હીરાનું ઉત્પાદન થઈ રહ્યું છે. જે ગુજરાતમાં તૈયાર થઈ રહ્યા છે. ગુજરાતમાં તેની 400 થી વધુ ફેક્ટરીઓ છે. તેને તૈયાર કરવામાં પર્યાવરણને કોઈ નુકસાન થતું નથી, તેથી જ તેને ઈકો-ફ્રેન્ડલી અથવા ગ્રીન ડાયમંડ કહેવામાં આવે છે.

આ રીતે બને છે તે: સામાન્ય રીતે, પૃથ્વી પરના કાર્બન કણો પર પડેલું દબાણ હીરોના નિર્માણ માટે જવાબદાર હોય છે, તેવી જ રીતે લેબમાં પણ એક ખાસ પ્રકારનું દબાણ બનાવવામાં આવે છે. કાર્બન કણો પર ખાસ પ્રકારનું દબાણ અને તાપમાન હીરાને તૈયાર કરે છે.
સર્ટિફાઇડ ડાયમંડઃ પીએમ મોદીએ જીલ બાઈડેનને જે હીરો આપ્યો હતો તે આ ટેકનિકથી બનાવવામાં આવ્યો હતો. આ હીરા જેમોલોજીકલ લેબમાંથી પ્રમાણિત છે. તેમાં 4-C હોલમાર્ક છે. જેના પર કટ, કલર, કેરેટ અને ક્લેરિટી જેવા ચાર પેરામીટર્સ (C) પર ટેસ્ટિંગ બાદ સ્ટેમ્પ લગાવવામાં આવ્યો છે.
કાશ્મીરનું પેપિયર મૈસે ખાસ વાત એ છે કે જે બોક્સમાં ગ્રીન હીરો રાખવામાં આવે છે તેને પેપિયર મેસે કહેવામાં આવે છે. તેને કાશ્મીરમાં તૈયાર કરવામાં આવ્યું છે. ત્યાંની કલાની છાપ તેના પર દેખાય છે.

टायटॅनिक पाहण्यासाठी गेलेली पाणबुडी सापडली ; अखेर पाणबुडीतील पाचही जणांचा मृत्यू 

बोस्टन :  बेपत्ता टायटन पाणबुडीबाबत मोठी बातमी समोर आली आहे. शोध पथकाला टायटॅनिक जहाजाजवळ हरवलेल्या पाणबुडीचे अवशेष सापडले आहेत. बेपत्ता टायटन पाणबुडीतील पाचही प्रवाशांचा मृत्यू झाल्याचं जहाज ऑपरेट करणाऱ्या कंपनीने म्हटलं आहे. टायटन पाणबुडीतील पाचही जणांचा दुर्दैवी मृत्यू झाला आहे. 

यूएस कोस्ट गार्डच्या अधिकाऱ्यांनी गुरुवारी पाचही प्रवाशांचा मृत्यू झाला आहे या गोष्टीला दुजोरा दिला. यूएस कोस्ट गार्डचे आर अॅडमिरल जॉन माउगर म्हणाले "अटलांटिक महासागरात टायटॅनिकच्या अवशेषाच्या खाली १६०० फूट खाली पाणबुडीचा मलबा सापडला आहे. रिमोटवर चालणाऱ्या वाहनातून हे शोधण्यात आले. पाणबुडीत स्फोट झाला असण्याची शक्यता आहे. 

पाणबुडी चालवणारी कंपनी ओशन गेट ने श्रद्धांजली वाहिली आहे. रॉयटर्सने दिलेल्या माहितीनुसार, भारतीय वेळेनुसार रविवारी संध्याकाळी साडेपाच वाजता ही पाणबुडी अटलांटिक महासागरात सोडण्यात आली. तासाभरानंतर ती बेपत्ता झाली. चार दिवसांपासून शोधमोहीम सुरू होती. पाणबुडीतील सर्व लोक बुडालेल्या टायटॅनिक जहाजाचे अवशेष पाहण्यासाठी खोल समुद्रात गेले होते, मात्र तिथे त्यांचा संपर्क तुटला. यूएस कोस्ट गार्डच्या म्हणण्यानुसार पाणबुडीचे अवशेष सापडल्यानंतर तज्ज्ञांच्या पथकाने तपास सुरू केला आहे. कॅनडाच्या एका जहाजात बसलेल्या मानवरहित रोबोटने पाणबुडीचे अवशेष शोधून काढले असल्याचं सांगितलं जात आहे.

टायटन पाणबुडीवर बसलेले पाचही लोक सुप्रसिद्ध अब्जाधीश होते. त्यात ओशन गेटचे सीईओ स्टॉकटन रश, प्रिन्स दाऊद आणि त्यांचा मुलगा सुलेमान दाऊद, हमिश हार्डिंग आणि पॉल-हेनरी नार्जियोलेट यांचा समावेश होता. १८ जून रोजी अमेरिकन कंपनी ओशनगेटची ही पाणबुडी टायटॅनिकचे अवशेष दाखवण्यासाठी प्रवासाला निघाली. या मलब्यापर्यंत पोहोचणं, तिथे फिरणं आणि नंतर परत येणं, असा टायटॅनिकचा टूर सुमारे आठ तास चालतो. मात्र हे पाचही जण परत येऊ शकले नाही.

शाई होप ने तोड़ा विराट कोहली के शतकों का 'ये' रिकॉर्ड, बाबर आजम है लिस्ट में नंबर-1

वेस्टइंडीज वनडे टीम के कप्तान शाई होप 50 ओवर फॉर्मेट में सबसे कम पारियों में 15 शतक ठोकने वाले तीसरे खिलाड़ी बन गए हैं। गुरुवार को वर्ल्ड कप क्वालीफायर में नेपाल के खिलाफ उन्होंने सेंचुरी लगाकर विराट कोहली का रिकॉर्ड तोड़ा। वनडे क्रिकेट में होप ने 15वां शतक 105वीं पारी में जड़ा, वहीं इस फॉर्मेट में 46 शतक जड़ने वाले किंग कोहली ने पहली 15 सेंचुरी के लिए 106 पारियां ली थी। 

पाकिस्तान के कप्तान बाबर आजम इस सूची के टॉप पर हैं। उन्होंने सबसे कम 83 पारियों में यह कारनामा किया था। वहीं उनके पीछे साउथ अफ्रीका के पूर्व क्रिकेट हाशिम अमला 86 पारियों के साथ मौजूद हैं।

वनडे क्रिकेट में सबसे तेज 15 शतक ठोकने वाले बल्लेबाज (पारियों के हिसाब से)
83 पारियां - बाबर आजम
86 पारियां - हाशिम आमला
105 पारियां - शाई होप
106 पारियां - विराट कोहली
108 पारियां - शिखर धवन और डेविड वॉर्नर

शाई होप ने अपनी इस पारी के दम पर एक और रिकॉर्ड भी अपने नाम किया। 2019 वर्ल्ड पक के बाद सबसे ज्यादा शतक जड़ने के मामले में उन्होंने बाबर आजम को पछाड़ नंबर-1 का पायदान हासिल कर लिया है। पिछले वर्ल्ड कप के बाद से होप के बल्ले से यह 9वां शतक निकला है, वहीं बाबर आजम इस सूची में 8 शतक के साथ दूसरे पायदान पर हैं।

वहीं इस मामले में तीसरे नंबर पर पाकिस्तान के ही फखर जमां हैं, जिन्होंने छह शतक लगाए हैं। भारतीय पूर्व कप्तान विराट कोहली और आयरलैंड के पॉल स्टर्लिंग इस सूची में 5-5 शतकों के साथ संयुक्त रूप से चौथे पायदान पर हैं। वहीं पांचवे नंबर पर भारतीय सलामी बल्लेबाज शुभमन गिल का नाम है जिन्होंने 4 सेंचुरी लगाई है।

According to new data released on Friday, the number of diabetics worldwide would more than double to 1.3 billion by the year 2050 as a result of structural racism and stark inter-country disparity.

New research predicts that the global number of people suffering from diabetes will double to 1.3 billion by 2050, driven by structural racism and inequality between countries. A study published in the Lancet journal found that high body mass index is linked to over half of diabetes deaths and disability. 

Factors such as diets, exercise, smoking, and alcohol also contribute to the increase. By 2045, three-quarters of adults with diabetes will live in low- and middle-income countries. 

However, diabetes rates are almost 1.5 times higher among minorities, even in wealthy countries like the United States. The Lancet argues that fighting diabetes requires long-term planning, investment, and attention from countries worldwide.
